e cheat sheet<\/span><\/strong> to see what it looks like when your succulents need more or less water. <span style=\"color: #7e913b;\"><span class=\"tve-leads-two-step-trigger tl-2step-trigger-43359\">Click here to grab that, it'll be super helpful.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18918\" style=\"width: 745px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18918\" class=\"wp-image-18918 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/05\/Discover-the-best-way-to-water-succulents-indoors-and-out.jpg\" alt=\"Discover the best way to water succulents indoors and out!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" data-pin-description=\"Watering Succulents: Wondering how often you should be watering your succulents? Find out all the ins and outs of how to water succulents with the tips in this post. You\u2019ll be surprised at how much water these drought tolerant plants need! #succulents #succulentgarden #water #wateringsucculents #howtowatersucculents #howoftentowatersucculents #succulentplanters #plantcare #indoorsucculents #outdoorsucculents #succulentleaves #succulenthouseplants #diysucculentprojects #succulentandcactus\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/05\/Discover-the-best-way-to-water-succulents-indoors-and-out-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/05\/Discover-the-best-way-to-water-succulents-indoors-and-out-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/05\/Discover-the-best-way-to-water-succulents-indoors-and-out-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/05\/Discover-the-best-way-to-water-succulents-indoors-and-out-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/05\/Discover-the-best-way-to-water-succulents-indoors-and-out-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-conten